109
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,140
What do you want?

110
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:52,660
Debts must be repaid.

111
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:54,100
It's only fair.

112
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:00,390
However...

113
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:02,100
(Loan Agreement)

114
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:02,830
I still consider

115
00:08:03,430 --> 00:08:06,070
Deng Xing a good brother.

116
00:08:06,540 --> 00:08:07,120
How about this?

117
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:10,310
Help me gamble a few more rounds.

118
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:12,100
You'll clear the debt

119
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:13,700
in no time.

120
